1ï¸âƒ£ Advanced Sequence Diagram (Audit-Ready Version)

Includes:

Status transitions

Audit trail updates

Notifications

Rejection loop


sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Maker
    actor Checker
    actor Controller
    participant System as BC&OR Portal
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Maker->>System: Create Plan (Draft)
    System->>Audit: Log Plan Creation

    Maker->>System: Submit Plan
    System->>Audit: Log Submission
    System-->>Checker: Notification

    Checker->>System: Review Plan

    alt Checker Rejects
        Checker->>System: Reject with Remarks
        System->>Audit: Log Rejection
        System-->>Maker: Return with Comments
    else Checker Approves
        Checker->>System: Approve
        System->>Audit: Log Checker Approval
        System-->>Controller: Forward for Final Approval

        Controller->>System: Review Plan

        alt Controller Rejects
            Controller->>System: Reject with Remarks
            System->>Audit: Log Controller Rejection
            System-->>Maker: Return with Comments
        else Controller Approves
            Controller->>System: Final Approval
            System->>Audit: Log Final Approval
            System-->>Maker: Plan Successfully Approved
        end
    end

âœ” Shows compliance traceability
âœ” Clear escalation structure
âœ” Suitable for Audit Committee presentation


