2ï¸âƒ£ Enterprise Activity Diagram (Swimlane Style)

More interactive with role separation.

flowchart LR

subgraph Maker
A1[Create Plan]
A2[Submit Plan]
A3[Modify Plan]
end

subgraph Checker
B1[Review Plan]
B2[Approve]
B3[Reject]
end

subgraph Controller
C1[Review Plan]
C2[Final Approve]
C3[Reject]
end

subgraph System
S1[(Update Status)]
S2[(Send Notification)]
S3[(Audit Log Update)]
end

Start((Start)) --> A1
A1 --> A2
A2 --> S1
S1 --> S3
S3 --> B1

B1 -->|Reject| B3 --> S1 --> S3 --> A3
B1 -->|Approve| B2 --> S1 --> S3 --> C1

C1 -->|Reject| C3 --> S1 --> S3 --> A3
C1 -->|Approve| C2 --> S1 --> S3 --> End((Approved))

âœ” Clearly separated responsibilities
âœ” Shows system automation
âœ” Highlights audit logging


