4ï¸âƒ£ State Machine Diagram (Very Important for Audit)

This is highly appreciated in audit presentations.

stateDiagram-v2

[*] --> Draft

Draft --> Submitted : Submit Plan
Submitted --> Rejected : Checker Reject
Rejected --> Draft : Modify

Submitted --> CheckerApproved : Checker Approve
CheckerApproved --> Rejected : Controller Reject
CheckerApproved --> ControllerApproved : Controller Approve

ControllerApproved --> [*]

âœ” Clearly shows lifecycle
âœ” Easy for compliance teams
âœ” Very clean for board-level presentation


